  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC432">
        <l>viṉaiyeñcu kiḷavikku viṉaiyuṅ kuṟippu</l>
	<l>niṉaiyat tōṉṟiya muṭipā kummē</l>
	<l>yāvayiṟ kuṟippē yākkamoṭu varumē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/238/mode/1up">238</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/239/mode/1up">239</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, niṟutta muṟaiyāṉē viṉaiyeccattiṟku muṭipu kūṟutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : viṉaiyeccam muṭiyuṅkāl viṉaiyum viṉaikkuṟippuṅ koṇṭu muṭiyum ; avviṭattuk kuṟippuviṉaiccol ākkaccolloṭu varum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : 'uḻutu vantāṉ' eṉpatu, viṉaiyeccam terinilai viṉaikoṇṭu muṭintatu..  'maruntu uṇṭu nallaṉāyiṉāṉ' eṉpatu, viṉaiyeccam viṉaikkuṟippuk koṇṭu muṭintatu ; avviṭattu viṉaikkuṟippu ākkamoṭu vantavāṟu kaṇṭukoḷka.</p>
<p>iṉi, 'niṉaiyat tōṉṟiya' eṉṟataṉāṉ, 'uḻutu varutal' 'uḻutu vantāṉ' eṉat toḻiṟpeyarāṉum muṭiyum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>maṟṟu, ic cūttirattāl viṉaiyeccattiṟku muṭipu kūṟavēṇṭiyatu eṉṉai ? viṉaiyiyaluḷ,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC432-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'mutaṉilai mūṉṟum viṉaimutal muṭipiṉa'</l></lg>	<p>[tol.viṉai-31]</p>
<p>eṉṟu moḻintaṉavaṟṟukku,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC432-Iḷam-cit2">
<l>'ēṉai yeccam viṉaimuta lāṉum</l>
<l>āṉvan tiyaiyum viṉainilai yāṉum'</l></lg>	<p>[tol.viṉai-33]</p>
<p>muṭiyumeṉṟu kūṟiyatē amaiyum piṟaveṉiṉ, ataṟku viṭai, āṇṭu, viṉaimutalāṉum muṭiyumeṉpuḻip peyar viṉaimutalāṉum muṭiyum eṉpatu paṭṭatu ; eṉṉai, viṉai viṉaimutaleṉṟum, peyar viṉaimutal eṉṟum pakarātu, potuvakaiyāṟ kūṟiṉārākaliṉ ic cūttiram vēṇṭum; itu kūṟākkāl, uḻutu cāttaṉ eṉap peyar mutal viṉaimutalāṉum muṭivāṉ cellum eṉpatu. aṉṟiyum, viṉaiyeccattiṟku viṉaikkuṟippu muṭipāṅkāl, ākkamoṭuvarutal eṭuttōta vēṇṭum eṉpatu.</p>
    </body>
  </text>

